high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Return to where you got the spatula from.
Put the spatula on the table under the let ice cream scoop.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the table.

high_descs: Make a right and walk towards the wooden table.
Pick up the spatula on the wooden table.
Make a right and walk towards the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink, removing it again.
Turn around to walk back towards the wooden table.
Set the spatula down on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a spatula in the sink to put it back on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn  right and walk straight to the table
Pick up the turner on the left side of the table
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the turner in the sink and rinse it
Turn around then head to the table
Put the turner on the table beside the potato
anns.task_desc: Put the clean turner on the table
